h4. Actor:
Configuration Manager.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Settings|guide:_ShowApplicationPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Development" sub menu from left menu.
* Click *System Configuration* link.
* [Show Landing Page of System Configuration|guide:ShowSysConfigurationActionService].
* Select a Line-Item from grid view.
* Click "Edit" button from tool bar.
* Open *System Configuration* in Edit Mode.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Select system configuration" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Get *System Configuration* details from server.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show selected *System Configuration* information in input form.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].
